      </p>

      <div style="font-size:.975rem; line-height:1.75; color:var(--text)">
        <p>
          These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of Tree Service News, located at <a href="https://treeservicenews.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--green); font-weight:600">https://treeservicenews.com</a>, and any related tools, applications, content, or services provided by Tree Service News ("we," "our," or "us").
        </p>
        <p>
          By using our website or services, you agree to these Terms.
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--black); margin:2rem 0 .75rem">
