          <li>Use the website or services for illegal, harmful, misleading, or abusive purposes</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
          <li>Interfere with website security or functionality</li>
          <li>Submit false, misleading, infringing, or unlawful content</li>
          <li>Use our services to spam, harass, or mislead others</li>
          <li>Violate the terms of any connected third-party platform, including Meta or Facebook</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--black); margin:2rem 0 .75rem">
          2. Content on Tree Service News
        </h2>
        <p>
          Tree Service News may publish articles, resources, summaries, commentary, links, or other informational content related to the tree service industry.
        </p>
        <p>
          Content is provided for general informational purposes only. We do not guarantee that all information is complete, accurate, current, or applicable to your specific situation.
        </p>
        <p>
          You should independently verify information before relying on it for business, legal, safety, financial, or operational decisions.
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--black); margin:2rem 0 .75rem">
          3. User-Submitted Content
        </h2>
        <p>
          If you submit content, links, business information, comments, messages, or other materials to us, you represent that you have the right to provide that content.
        </p>
        <p>
          You grant us permission to use, display, edit, publish, or distribute submitted content as reasonably necessary to operate and promote Tree Service News and related services.
        </p>
        <p>
          You are responsible for ensuring that your submitted content does not violate any law, copyright, trademark, privacy right, or third-party agreement.
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--black); margin:2rem 0 .75rem">
          4. Social Media and Facebook Page Posting
        </h2>
        <p>
          If you connect a Facebook Page or other social media account to our services, you authorize us to perform the actions you approve, such as publishing or scheduling posts.
        </p>
        <p>
          You are responsible for reviewing and approving any content before it is posted unless you have specifically authorized automated posting.
        </p>
        <p>
          You agree that you will comply with Meta's terms, platform policies, community standards, and any applicable advertising or content rules.
        </p>
        <p>
          We are not responsible for actions taken by Meta, Facebook, or other third-party platforms, including rejected posts, account restrictions, API changes, outages, or permission changes.
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--black); margin:2rem 0 .75rem">
          5. Third-Party Links and Services
        </h2>
        <p>
          Our website may contain links to third-party websites, tools, articles, products, or services.
        </p>
        <p>
          We do not control third-party websites and are not responsible for their content, privacy practices, accuracy, availability, or policies.
