        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--black); margin:2rem 0 .75rem">
          7. No Professional Advice
        </h2>
        <p>
          Content on Tree Service News is not legal, financial, insurance, safety, medical, or professional advice.
        </p>
        <p>
          Tree service work can involve significant risk. Any safety-related or operational content should be reviewed against applicable laws, regulations, industry standards, manufacturer instructions, and qualified professional guidance.
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--black); margin:2rem 0 .75rem">
          8. Disclaimer of Warranties
        </h2>
        <p>Our website and services are provided "as is" and "as available."</p>
        <p>We make no warranties or guarantees regarding:</p>
        <ul style="margin:0 0 1.5rem; padding-left:1.25rem; display:grid; gap:.35rem">
          <li>Website availability</li>
          <li>Accuracy of content</li>
          <li>Fitness for a particular purpose</li>
          <li>Results from using our services</li>
          <li>Compatibility with third-party platforms</li>
          <li>Continued availability of APIs or integrations</li>
        </ul>
