        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--black); margin:2rem 0 .75rem">
          13. Termination
        </h2>
        <p>
          We may restrict or terminate access to our website or services if we believe you have violated these Terms, misused the service, or created risk for us, other users, or third-party platforms.
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--black); margin:2rem 0 .75rem">
          14. Governing Law
        </h2>
        <p>
          These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Texas, without regard to conflict of law principles.
        </p>
        <p>
          Any disputes will be handled in the appropriate courts located in Texas, unless otherwise required by law.
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--black); margin:2rem 0 .75rem">
          15. Changes to These Terms
        </h2>
        <p>
          We may update these Terms from time to time. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.
        </p>
        <p>
          Continued use of the website or services after changes are posted means you accept the updated Terms.
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.25rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--black); margin:2rem 0 .75rem">
          16. Contact Us
        </h2>
        <p>If you have questions about these Terms, contact us at:</p>
        <p>
